ackup 檔 backup 咗d app data, ,再從 app store 扯返隻 app 落黎<br />\n<br />\n總之結論係 restore 完等佢自動 wifi load 一輪野... 屋企 wifi 慢要考慮下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋要入返 apple id, touch id, wallet.. 暫時諗到係咁多"},{"pid":"90c258b33bb9232e10091082402cb53401a75edb","tid":903250,"uid":109383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"39fb12b5c08e10c327044e2efe9dfcef81cf3170","tid":903250,"uid":214111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T16:00:20.000Z","msg":"啱啱試左, 原來個 backup 都唔算 full backup, 要 wifi download 返d app.. <br />\n<br />\n唔肯定個 backup 檔係 back 咗 d app, 再從 icloud 扯返d app data 落黎 定係 個 backup 檔 backup 咗d app data, ,再從 app store 扯返隻 app 落黎<br />\n<br />\n總之結論係 restore 完等佢自動 wifi load 一輪野... 屋企 wifi 慢要考慮下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋要入返 apple id, touch id, wallet.. 暫時諗到係咁多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T16:03:14.000Z","msg":"你download完app 會發覺唔洗再登入過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b80d09224c28a8f2e7db2c9ee2f075bb9f1497a","tid":903250,"uid":215398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T16:06:31.000Z","msg":"基本所有都係到 除左啲wts sticker同apple music要down 其他佢會自動係背景到更新<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 只要洗機或換機之前backup就成部機就會一樣咁copy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9e3e376fb4450ecf20da5ae2d19606bb0d40474","tid":903250,"uid":83748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T16:13:21.000Z","msg":"但銀行app pw <br />\n機票app acc<br />\nApple Pay d card都要重入過嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c3d171957a5c52413fac64c86d4e24f411cf5a6","tid":903250,"uid":214111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9e3e376fb4450ecf20da5ae2d19606bb0d40474","tid":903250,"uid":83748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T16:13:21.000Z","msg":"但銀行a